### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَقَالَتْ أُولَىٰهُمْ لِأُخْرَىٰهُمْ فَمَا كَانَ لَكُمْ عَلَيْنَا مِن فَضْلٍ فَذُوقُوا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَكْسِبُونَ</span>

### English

Then the leaders will say to their followers, “You were no better than us! So taste the torment for what you used to commit.”